OL,3,CMan who was nearly sucked out of
OL,4,CRyanair plane says he is 'mentally
OL,5,Cdestroyed'
OL,7,FLjubisa Karovic who was nearly sucked
OL,8,Fthrough a broken window on a Ryanair
OL,9,Fflight, says he is grateful that he
OL,10,Fsurvived but is still struggling with
OL,11,Fhis ordeal, ITV News Correspondent
OL,12,FNeil Connery reports
OL,14,FThe man who survived nearly being
OL,15,Fsucked out of a mid-air Ryanair flight
OL,16,Fhas said he is traumatised by the
OL,17,Fexperience and faces a long road to
OL,18,Frecovery.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
