OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784722711
OL,3,CMan who was nearly sucked out of
OL,4,CRyanair plane says he is 'mentally
OL,5,Cdestroyed'
OL,7,FSpeaking from Greece, Serbian national
OL,8,FLjubisa Karovic shared his story with
OL,9,FGerman newspaper Bild, saying: "As
OL,10,Fsoon as I close my eyes, I see
OL,11,Fpictures of what I experienced, those
OL,12,Ffew minutes, it's a nightmare.
OL,14,FHe said he was asleep when the window
OL,15,Fwas breached, saying he was woken by
OL,16,Fwhat sounded like a bomb going off.
OL,18,F"For a moment I was conscious, but
OL,19,Fthen I don't remember anything until
OL,20,Fthey woke me - I was covered in blood."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
