PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784722711
OL,3,CMan who was nearly sucked out of
OL,4,CRyanair plane says he is 'mentally
OL,5,Cdestroyed'
OL,7,FThe incident happened soon after take-
OL,8,Foff on a Boeing 737-800 aircraft which
OL,9,Fdeparted the Greek city of
OL,10,FThessaloniki bound for Memmingen,
OL,11,FGermany.
OL,13,FThe plane was forced to turn around
OL,14,Fand make an emergency landing back in
OL,15,FThessaloniki.
OL,17,FKarovic suffered numerous friction
OL,18,Fburns and serious injuries to his
OL,19,Fspine and shoulder.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
