FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784722711
OL,3,CMan who was nearly sucked out of
OL,4,CRyanair plane says he is 'mentally
OL,5,Cdestroyed'
OL,7,FHe said: "I can't go out, everything
OL,8,Fbothers me, mentally I am destroyed,
OL,9,Fthis has had a huge impact on my life.
OL,10,FWhenever I hear the sound of a plane,
OL,11,FI become stressed."
OL,13,FHe was discharged from hospital last
OL,14,Fweek and is currently recovering in a
OL,15,Frented villa near Thessaloniki with
OL,16,Fhis wife, Svetlana Grkovic.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
