PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784722711
OL,3,CMan who was nearly sucked out of
OL,4,CRyanair plane says he is 'mentally
OL,5,Cdestroyed'
OL,7,FMs Grkovic previously told the Serbian
OL,8,Fmedia outlet Nova she grabbed her
OL,9,Fhusband the moment the window smashed,
OL,10,Fand held onto his legs to stop him
OL,11,Ffrom being dragged out of the plane.
OL,13,F"I reacted immediately and grabbed his
OL,14,Flegs. I thought: 'If we die, we die
OL,15,Ftogether.' It was horrible," she told
OL,16,Fthe publication.
OL,18,FShe said many passengers were
OL,19,Fparalysed with fear, but several came
OL,20,Fto help and together they managed to
OL,21,Fcling onto her husband.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784722711
OL,3,CMan who was nearly sucked out of
OL,4,CRyanair plane says he is 'mentally
OL,5,Cdestroyed'
OL,7,FDoctors have said his recovery will
OL,8,Ftake months and he may still need
OL,9,Fsurgery.
OL,11,FRyanair boss Michael O'Leary said
OL,12,Finitial reports indicate a "foreign
OL,13,Fobject" appeared to hit the plane's
OL,14,Fengine, causing a fan blade to snap
OL,15,Foff and hit the window, causing a
OL,16,F"depressurisation event."
OL,18,FHe said the engine had been fully
OL,19,Fserviced in the past two years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
