PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784722711
OL,3,CMan who was nearly sucked out of
OL,4,CRyanair plane says he is 'mentally
OL,5,Cdestroyed'
OL,7,FRyanair said in a statement after the
OL,8,Fincident: "A Ryanair flight from
OL,9,FThessaloniki to Memmingen on Friday
OL,10,Fmorning (10 July) returned to
OL,11,FThessaloniki shortly after take-off
OL,12,Fwhen a passenger window dislodged
OL,13,Finflight.
OL,15,F"The aircraft landed normally and
OL,16,Fpassengers returned to the terminal.
OL,17,FOne passenger requested and received
OL,18,Fmedical assistance on the ground in
OL,19,FThessaloniki."
OL,26,@pD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
