OL,3,CMan who was nearly sucked out of
OL,4,CRyanair plane says he is 'mentally
OL,5,Cdestroyed'
OL,7,FRyanair found a replacement aircraft,
OL,8,Fand the other passengers on the plane
OL,9,Fwere able to complete their journey
OL,10,Fthe same day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
